## Evaluation Criteria

Ideas are rated on:

| Criterion | What It Means |
|-----------|---------------|
| **Viability** | High/Medium/Low - Can this realistically make money? |
| **Effort** | Low/Medium/High - Time/capital to launch |
| **Alignment** | How well does this fit existing skills and projects? |
| **Moat** | Is there defensibility or just a race to the bottom? |
| **Revenue Model** | One-time, recurring, or hybrid |

